sentence: what are the flights from charlotte to atlanta returning on tuesday july thirteenth
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v0.flight_id||'"', '"'||v1.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.state_code||'"',
 '"'||v3.state_name||'"', '"'||v4.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v5.city_code||'"', '"'||v5.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v6.days_code||'"', '"'||v7.day_name||'"', v7.year, v7.month_number,
 v7.day_number FROM flight v0, airport_service v1,
 city v2, state v3, airport_service v4, city v5, days v6,
 date_day v7 
WHERE (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) 
AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code) AND ((v2.city_name = 'CHARLOTTE') 
AND ((v2.state_code = ANY v3.state_code) AND (v3.state_name = 'NORTH CAROLINA'))))) 
AND (((v0.to_airport = ANY v4.airport_code) 
AND ((v4.city_code = ANY v5.city_code) 
AND (v5.city_name = 'ATLANTA'))) AND ((v0.flight_days = ANY v6.days_code) 
AND ((v6.day_name = ANY v7.day_name) AND (((v7.year =  1993) 
AND (v7.month_number =  7)) AND (v7.day_number =  13))))));

FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS .
